Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.70,0:00:30.89,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Love，I've got to feel it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.03,0:00:34.16,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}If you put your trust in me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.32,0:00:37.55,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}I know what my life would be
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.65,0:00:42.60,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Oh，you are all I ever need
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.66,0:00:48.19,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}I try to hear what you say
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.30,0:00:50.43,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}So I pray
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.44,0:00:54.22,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}But you're fading away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.42,0:01:01.45,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Don't go and break my fragile heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.67,0:01:04.93,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}We won't fall apart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.93,0:01:12.86,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}'Cause you're my only star
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.88,0:01:18.62,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}I wonder why my tears come at night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.66,0:01:22.15,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Calling you，so like a little child
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.30,0:01:25.57,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}All the things you have in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.68,0:01:28.71,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}I wish I could see your insides
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.82,0:01:31.78,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}My love，you've got to feel it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.78,0:01:35.27,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}And if we put our trust in you and me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.28,0:01:38.74,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}You know what our lives would be
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.88,0:01:46.15,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1000)}Oh，you are the one I believe
