Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.60,0:22:30.07,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}笑顔は未来に続いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.50,0:21:34.74,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}微微  清风徐来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.38,0:21:42.04,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}飒飒  漫逐云端
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.41,0:21:49.18,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}音色交织  光灿闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.39,0:21:52.69,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}纵是凋落的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.92,0:22:00.22,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}定有重拾的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.52,0:22:08.59,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}紧紧拥抱你的余音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.50,0:22:15.41,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}牢牢握住牵你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.50,0:22:22.54,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}勿忘  该重视的一切
